Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support

This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeQueryParentDef All defs that can parent a query construct should implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
AeAssignCopyDef Holds individual copy operations of an assign activity
AeConditionDef Models the 'condition' bpel construct that is a child of the 'if' construct.
AeCorrelationDef Holds individual correlation elements
AeCorrelationDef.AeCorrelationPatternType Type for the correlation pattern.
AeCorrelationDef.AeInvalidCorrelationPatternType Type for an invalid correlation pattern.
AeElseDef Models the 'else' construct in WS-BPEL 2.0 in addition to the 'otherwise' construct in BPEL4WS 1.1.
AeElseIfDef Models the 'elseIf' construct in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeExpressionBaseDef Base class for all defs that specify an expression, such as transitionCondition, joinCondition, etc...
AeExtensibleAssignDef Models the extensibleAssign construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeForDef Models the 'wait' | 'onAlarm' constructs 'for' child element introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeForEachBranchesDef Branches def resides under the optional completionCondition for the serial and parallel forEach.
AeForEachCompletionConditionDef Models the optional completion def that resides under a serial or parallel forEach.
AeForEachFinalDef Models the final expression for a forEach
AeForEachStartDef Models the start expression for a forEach
AeFromDef Models the from element in a copy operation or variable initialization.
AeFromPartDef Models the invoke|receive|onMessage|onEvent 'fromPart' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeFromPartsDef Models the BPEL 2.0 'fromParts' construct.
AeIfDef A wrapper class for the condition and activity child defs of the if activity.
AeJoinConditionDef Models the 'joinCondition' construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeLinkDef Definition for link objects which are in support of the flow activity definition.
AeLinksDef Container for the links within a Flow.
AeLiteralDef Models the new literal bpel construct wrapper introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeOnAlarmDef The onAlarm element used within the Pick activity
AeOnEventDef Models the 'onEvent' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeOnMessageDef The onMessage element used within the Pick activity
AeQueryDef Models the query construct that was introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0 as a child of the from and to constructs.
AeRepeatEveryDef Models the 'repeatEvery' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeSourceDef Definition base for all named definition elements
AeSourcesDef Models the 'sources' container bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeTargetDef Definition base for all named definition elements
AeTargetsDef Models the 'target' container bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeToDef Models the to element in a copy operation.
AeToPartDef Models the invoke|reply activity's 'toPart' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeToPartsDef Models the BPEL 2.0 'toParts' construct.
AeTransitionConditionDef Models the 'transitionCondition' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeUntilDef Models the 'wait' | 'onAlarm' constructs 'until' child element introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeVarDef Assign activity support class, variables for copying information.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support Description

This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities. These classes are used within the activity definitions and help support the creation and manipulation of those objects.
